{"build_type":"library","description":"Channel B gate foundation. Brings up the shared portal region and its paired request/response eventfds, reusing the proven serve-offset-region-portal sequence: create two eventfds; memfd_create vehirgw with sealing; ftruncate to 16384; add seals; mmap MAP_SHARED of the memfd as the shared region base; dup2 so the region descriptor is fd 5, the request eventfd is fd 3, the response eventfd is fd 4 (the fd3/fd4/fd5 convention any inherited child knows). Records the region base and size in g_portal_region_base and g_portal_region_size for in-kernel code, and returns the base. Additive Channel B foundation; does not touch Channel A.","module_name":"install-offset-region-portal-bearing-eventfd-descriptor","package_name":"install-offset-region-portal-bearing-eventfd-descriptor","function_definitions":{"install-offset-region-portal-bearing-eventfd-descriptor":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"three","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":3},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"four","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"five","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"prot","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":3},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"mapshared","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declara